Manchester United Board Had No Talks, Says Soccer Club `Not For Sale'

-- B y   T a r i q   P a n j a
-- 
2011-02-25T11:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/manchester-united-board-had-no-talks-says-soccer-club-not-for-sale-.html
Manchester United’s board said the
club is “not for sale” and that “no discussions have taken
place,” according to a statement today.  The club also reported total quarterly revenue of 93.2
million pounds, up from 87 million pounds in the year earlier
period.  To contact the reporter on this story:
